Purchase options and add-ons

  • Efficient Treatment Nebulizer Machine - Better nebulization effect, the nebulized particles are around 0.5-5m. The tiny mist can reach the affected area for treatment easier and faster, allowing your breathing problems to be treated while you breathe.Easier and more natural, and breathing treatment nebulizer that can be used by both adults and kids.
  • Digital Display Nebulizer - New timing function and LED digital display control,easy and simple to operate, 3 timing options are available, more accurate control of each treatment time.
  • Quiet Desktop Nebulizer - The nebulizer uses a new generation of silent motor, New generation of noise reduction technology, noise can be controlled 50dB. The bottom of the nebulizer is also equipped with shockproof foot pads,multiple shock absorption and noise reduction.
  • Long Service Life - This jet nebulizer directly using 120V/60Hz AC power connection, working time is not limited by time, you can cycle through different time periods to achieve your desired treatment time, low loss and more durable. Ideal for home use nebulizer.
  • Complete Accessories&Quality Warranty - An adult mask and a child mask are packed with the nebulizer for daily use of children and adults.       How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      4 Stars
      Really nice digital nebulizer!
      I like this digital nebulizer a lot! I have owned several nebulizers over the last 20 or so years that I have been using them, this one is cool! I love that it has a timer on it. I love how the nebulizer medicine cup has a thing to adjust the pressure of the medicine coming out. The reason I gave 4 stars is because I have to unplug it each time I'm finished using it because the lights never turn off! I am a huge electricity saver and this just isn't something I like. I want the lights to go off when I'm done... it costs a lot for electricity where I live, so I want to save as much as I possibly can! Other than that, I like this nebulizer. I would absolutely recommend this to everyone in need of one, and I would purchase again in the future!
